snippet.title: The Batmaniac
snippet.description: You want to learn all things Batman? You just found the right place! You want tributes? You will get tributes! Top 5 lists?  We got those as well! Interested in Bat-Universe comics analysis? Duh, this is a thing here too! More of a movie person? Don't worry we do both! Games? We love games! In fact we love everything about Batman! What are you waiting for? Become a Batmaniac as well and let's make history together.. Well, not history but I wanted to make it sound dramatic, you know?
